Name: Fly You Fly
About the game: Fly You Fly is a retro-styled v-scroller by Andrée Lindgren. Your mission is to find new homes for the Hugo family. They will have to travel far so make sure to keep your flies from starving while also avoiding all the obstacles and dangers ahead.
